OL,3,CHastings outage: Southern Water
OL,4,Cchallenged over pipe declared
OL,5,C'outworn' in 2007
OL,7,FITV News Meridian's Abigail Bracken
OL,8,Fchallenges Southern Water's Head of
OL,9,FCustomer service Ashley Marshman over
OL,10,Fclaims the company failed to repair an
OL,11,F'outworn' pipe in 2007
OL,13,FITV News can reveal that underground
OL,14,Fpiping which was declared 'outworn' 17
OL,15,Fyears ago was never replaced by
OL,16,FSouthern Water, after 30-thousand
OL,17,Fhomes in were left without supplies
OL,18,Ffollowing a burst main.
