OL,3,CHastings outage: Southern Water
OL,4,Cchallenged over pipe declared
OL,5,C'outworn' in 2007
OL,7,Fwas granted permission to upgrade a
OL,8,F12km main between the Darwell
OL,9,FReservoir and Beauport Water Supply
OL,10,FWorks in 2007.
OL,12,FThe company's application to Rother
OL,13,FDistrict Council said the works were
OL,14,Fneeded to ' 'improve the security of
OL,15,Fdrinking water supply to the Hastings
OL,16,Farea'.
OL,18,FDespite approval, the water firm did
OL,19,Fnot carry out the replacement with the
OL,20,Flocal council telling us that the
OL,21,Fcompany put the project 'on hold'.
