OL,7,FFollowing the accusations that the
OL,8,Forganisation failed to maintain the
OL,9,Fpipeline properly, Southern Water's
OL,10,FHead of Customer Service Ashley
OL,11,FMarshman told ITV News,
OL,13,F"We are aware of reports of this
OL,14,Fplanning application. What I will say
OL,15,Fis our focus right now is to get the
OL,16,Fremaining customers back in supply.
OL,18,F"As part of our pre-incident
OL,19,Finvestigation, we will be looking into
OL,20,Fthis and we'll report back to our
OL,21,Fcustomers on what that was all about."
