OL,4,Cchallenged over pipe declared
OL,5,C'outworn' in 2007
OL,7,FProperties and businesses in Hastings
OL,8,Fand St Leonards began experiencing
OL,9,Fproblems with their water supply on
OL,10,FThursday 2nd May after a pipe, deep in
OL,11,Fwoodland, ruptured.
OL,13,FSchools and colleges were forced to
OL,14,Fclose and businesses resorted to
OL,15,Fgathering water from the sea just to
OL,16,Fflush toilets.
OL,18,FHastings Town Centre Manager John
OL,19,FBownas said, "I was gobsmacked,
OL,20,Fabsolutely gobsmacked.
