OL,7,F"There's going to be huge questions
OL,8,Fasked now as to why, 15 years ago, a
OL,9,Fproblem was identified and nothing was
OL,10,Fdone about it."
OL,12,FEngineers have spent the last five
OL,13,Fdays repairing the pipe and restarting
OL,14,Fsupplies.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday 2,000 or so households woke
OL,17,Fup to low or no water supply, with
OL,18,Ftankers being drafted in to support
OL,19,Fthe network.
