OL,7,FSince the problems started, more than
OL,8,Fone million bottles of water have been
OL,9,Fhanded out to residents, the most its
OL,10,Fever delivered during an outage.
OL,12,FSouthern Water has apologised to
OL,13,Fcustomers and says it will compensate
OL,14,Fcustomers,
OL,16,F"Once we are confident that all our
OL,17,Fcustomers have their water supply
OL,18,Frestored and stable, we will explore
OL,19,Fcompensation options", a spokesperson
OL,20,Fsaid.
